@LingoCross.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5093

### Sağlık kontrolü
GET {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Kayıt (öğretmen)
POST {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ogretmen@example.com",
  "password": "Sifre1234!",
  "displayName": "Örnek Öğretmen",
  "role": 1
}

### Giriş
POST {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ogretmen@example.com",
  "password": "Sifre1234!"
}

### Token yenileme
POST {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "<refresh-token>"
}

### Çıkış
POST {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "<refresh-token>"
}

### Şifremi unuttum (her zaman 200)
POST {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ogretmen@example.com"
}

### Şifre sıfırlama (token dev log'undan)
POST {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "<reset-token>",
  "newPassword": "YeniSifre9!"
}

### Profilim (Bearer access token gerekir)
GET {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

###
